Q - the kind of quantity captured by the measure
Enclosing class:
VectorMeasure<Q extends Quantity<Q>>
public static class VectorMeasure.VectorMeasureBuilder<Q extends Quantity<Q>>
extends Object

Builder to create vector measure object. 

      VectorMeasure measure = new VectorMeasure.VectorMeasureBuilder()
          .sensor("gyroscope")
          .hasMeasured(new Acceleration(1))
          .hasMeasured(new Acceleration(2), new Acceleration(3))
          .at(new Date())
          .build();
